@startuml
!theme plain

title UIM Application Autoscaler (AAS) - Deployment Component View

node "Developer Workstation" as DevHost {
  component "Podman" as Podman
  artifact "uim-aas image" as Image
}

cloud "Container Registry" as Registry

node "Kubernetes Cluster" as Cluster {
  node "Namespace" as Namespace {
    component "Deployment\nuim-sap-aas" as Deployment
    component "ReplicaSet / Pods\nuim-sap-aas-service" as Pods
    component "Service\nuim-sap-aas" as Service
    component "HPA\nuim-sap-aas" as HPA
    component "ConfigMap\nuim-sap-aas-config" as ConfigMap
    component "Secret\nuim-sap-aas-secret" as Secret
  }

  component "Metrics Server" as Metrics
  component "Kubernetes API Server" as K8sAPI
}

cloud "Cloud Foundry API" as CFAPI

DevHost --> Podman : build/push image
Podman --> Image
Podman --> Registry : push
Registry --> Deployment : image pull

Deployment --> Pods : creates/updates
ConfigMap --> Pods : env config
Secret --> Pods : auth token
Service --> Pods : routes HTTP traffic
HPA --> Deployment : scales replicas
Metrics --> HPA : cpu/memory metrics

Pods --> CFAPI : CF scale adapter call\n(manual endpoint integration)
K8sAPI --> Deployment
K8sAPI --> Service
K8sAPI --> HPA

note right of Pods
Runtime container:
- vibe.d HTTP server
- policy evaluation engine
- in-memory app/policy store
end note

@enduml
